    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately not assessed per MRL 2 scoping. UQ demonstrates RH < 1 acceptance criterion holds at 95% confidence across characterized input uncertainties. The CFD model is deemed credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. Sensitivity analysis to characterize dominant input drivers is planned for future work and does not preclude acceptance at the current assessment level.",
